Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.00,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.93,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,今度こそ完璧にこなそう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.39,0:15:46.46,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,だって僕は　こんなにも期待されてる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.91,0:15:50.17,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世さんには僕しかいない　僕だけが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.53,JP - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,あの　これでいいんだっピよね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.53,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,僕だけが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.65,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,僕だけが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.52,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,いいんだよね　お母さん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.52,0:16:03.35,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,これできっと　僕はあなたみたいに
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.65,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,人を助けるお仕事に　
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.11,0:16:10.35,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,たくさんの人の命を助けるお　医者さんに　
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.10,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.44,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.69,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君　私ね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.25,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,私にはもう東君しかいないの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.57,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,だからずーっと待ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.94,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君が自首して少年院に入っても
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.73,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,私　ずっと待ってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.67,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,その間にチャッピー捜しておくから
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.00,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.84,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,ホント
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.15,0:16:56.29,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,ホントに久世さんは僕のこと　諦めないでくれる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.12,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.03,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,大丈夫　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.43,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.38,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,そういえば
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.52,0:17:22.40,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,お母さんが抱きしめてくれたのは　あの日が最後だったと思い出した
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.15,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.90,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,こんな早くにどこ行くんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.41,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.04,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,お前が殺したんだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.28,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,一家の面汚しが
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.88,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,お前のせいで何もかも台なしだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.89,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,母さんの病院も俺の将来も
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.41,0:18:07.28,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,無能なだけじゃなく足まで引っ張るのか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.20,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,どう責任取ってくれる
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.57,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.29,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.77,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,やっぱ何か思いつめてるだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.76,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,だからちゃんと相談しろって
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.53,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,何でも聞くから
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.92,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,お前には分からないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.41,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,有能　人格者で　何でもできて
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.46,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,みんな　お前のことばっかりだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.23,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,でも　僕には　誰もいない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.83,0:18:48.61,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,友達もつくらないで頑張ったのに　何もできなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.20,0:18:53.19,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,求められたことは　何一つできなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.82,0:18:58.59,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,母さんにだって　失望されて　諦められて
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.60,0:19:04.03,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,誰も僕に　興味なんかない　期待してない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.78,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,僕には　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.64,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世さんしか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.95,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.91,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,俺がいるだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.69,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,さっきから言ってるだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.11,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,何でも聞くっていうのはな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.48,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,テストの点がどうとか関係ねえんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.68,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,どうでもいいんだそんなことは
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.05,0:19:34.01,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,分かんないことだろうが悩みだろうが何でも言っていいし
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.15,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,聞きたいよ　俺は
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.55,0:19:40.83,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,お前は俺の　弟なんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.82,0:19:47.04,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,できないことは　できないって言っていいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.03,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,直樹
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.18,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,てかなあ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.48,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,何でもできるやつなんていないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.24,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,俺　モンハン下手だし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.86,0:20:11.04,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,ここだけの話　いっつも彼女に手伝ってもらってるし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.42,0:20:16.42,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,あと　母さんのパンケーキ　昔はめっちゃまずかった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.77,JP - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,ウソだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.11,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,ホントに
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.34,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,生焼けで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.34,0:20:25.45,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,でも夜勤前に作ってたから　冷蔵庫で逆に固まってて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.03,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,だから努力の人なんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.33,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,よく似てるよ　お前と
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.98,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.41,0:20:46.21,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,この眼鏡　母さんが買ってくれて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.42,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,もう度が合わないって言い出せなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.94,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.10,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,それで　それで僕　
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.85,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんに聞いてほしいことが　
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.57,JP - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,言わなきゃいけないことが　あるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.92,JP - down,Junya,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.81,0:21:30.59,JP - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,聞いたあそこの病院の子
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.98,JP - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,例の事件関わってたんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.63,JP - down,Neighbor B,0,0,0,,えー　本当
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.44,JP - down,Neighbor B,0,0,0,,あんな　いい子が
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.76,JP - down,Neighbor C,0,0,0,,誰かにやらされてたんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.98,JP - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,警察もそう見てるらしいわよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.45,JP - down,Neighbor C,0,0,0,,ひどーい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.45,0:21:47.00,JP - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,そうそう　何でもウワサだと　確か同級生の　
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.25,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.60,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君はもう助けてくれないんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.77,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.93,0:22:02.15,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,これからどうするっピか
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.82,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,ぼくたちも　もう本当のことを　
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.82,0:22:09.28,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,え　何言ってんの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.82,0:22:12.51,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,ピ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.07,0:22:16.09,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,今日から夏休みだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.93,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,そだっピか
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.81,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,だから行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.03,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東京
Comment: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.27,CN - down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.91,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那 那個 靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.76,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,今天的作戰會議就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.20,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:19.90,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,暑假很快就要到了 要好好準備才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:16.66,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.42,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我有話要說聽聽吧噼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:24.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,現在馬上解除變身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.27,CN - down,Both,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.17,CN - down,Newscaster,0,0,0,,根據警方公布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.93,CN - down,Newscaster,0,0,0,,死者是小學四年級學生 雲母坂麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:39.22,CN - down,Newscaster,0,0,0,,因其頭部具有受到明顯重擊的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.92,CN - down,Newscaster,0,0,0,,警方正以故意殺人案件為方向進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:57.66,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你 你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.61,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.99,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,今天我也要打工 媽媽她又拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:04.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我會做好的
Comment: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.99,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.94,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:28.46,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,正如老師剛剛所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:34.25,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,昨天 大家的朋友雲母坂麻里奈去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.48,CN - up,Marina's Friend B,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:38.14,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,雖然大家會非常難過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.72,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,但希望大家在力所能及的範圍幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:44.61,CN - down,Officer,0,0,0,,從現在開始 和警察的我們好好聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:51.98,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,畢竟屍體在記憶盒子裡 真正的死亡日期不會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.57,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,指紋也都擦除了 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.20,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,雖然地質勘探在預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但是問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,只要繼續這樣沉默下去就不會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.87,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:05.85,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.26,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,一直「沉默」下去真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.50,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.72,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我好考慮了很多噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:22.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的事情 還有今後的事情 我都想和大家談談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,已經暴露了啊 她屍體都被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:32.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,現在「說」也沒什麼用啊 你這死章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:39.90,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的爸爸媽媽 肯定也非常悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:44.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我認為我也要「力所能及」做些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:49.37,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,為了麻里奈 還有她的家人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.76,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,比起繼續隱瞞 說出真相的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.56,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.09,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,現在 只要全都實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.30,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶 不開作戰會議了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:08.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,很快暑假就到了 偷懶可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:14.24,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是 要是在這個時間離開這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:18.44,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君 能去的吧 東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:23.47,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,是你說過的吧 到暑假就能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.50,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:32.42,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,那 就 坐新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.26,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是啊 我得做好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我說了 我得做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:43.34,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,再者 屍體是我說要藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.84,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但是卻被發現了 我明明能做得更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.05,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不 沒關係 下次絕對能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,可以瞞天過海 可以前往東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那麼久世她就會 一直對我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.03,CN - up,Junya,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.31,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,這麼晚了還在學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:11.81,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 我有敲門哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:17.51,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,說起來 那個案件 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.02,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,是和你同班的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.71,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,她的朋友們應該很傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.37,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,班級裡的氣氛如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.04,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你也要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.81,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,如果有什麼事情儘管和我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.72,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,警察他們 是不是很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:43.39,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,說起來那個女生 是和你一起玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.49,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我 去個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.37,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,哦 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:58.92,CN - down,Marina's Friend D,0,0,0,,說起來 最近的麻里奈很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.42,CN - down,Marina's Friend C,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.30,CN - down,Police,0,0,0,,奇怪 在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.19,CN - down,Marina's Friend A,0,0,0,,那個 突然對某人點頭哈腰的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.46,CN - down,Marina's Friend D,0,0,0,,是啊 是不是被她抓住了什麼把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.93,CN - down,Marina's Friend A,0,0,0,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.07,CN - down,Police,0,0,0,,那人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.94,CN - down,Marina's Friend D,0,0,0,,是那個傢伙 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.69,CN - down,All,0,0,0,,久世同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.70,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我按照東君你說的 不明白的事情都沒有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.90,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,大家都認為犯人應該是大人 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.56,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是他們還會找我問話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.78,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒問題的吧暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.59,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,能去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.74,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.76,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒事的 絕對能去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,把不在場證明再好好準備一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,一直保持沉默挺奇怪的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:56.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊抱歉 說不用回答的人是我吧 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.25,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你絕對不會被懷疑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我一定 會做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.47,CN - down,Girl U,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.52,CN - down,Girl U,0,0,0,,測試結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.34,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.30,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,儘管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.94,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,你最近也挺辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.92,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,一直都在外面努力到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:12.79,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽 難不成她全部都 理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:18.13,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽 我 那個 有話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.87,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.34,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:28.33,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,就算「做不到」也沒必要每天假裝用功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:31.86,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,然後考個垃圾分數引人注意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:35.49,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽我不管怎麼說 都覺得這太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.87,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,所以 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.83,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,媽媽也不再努力管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.72,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,每天你都可以吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.73,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,多少分的成績也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.73,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,愛怎麼做就怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.26,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.91,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽 我還
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.22,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,那 請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.78,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.07,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,剛剛警察又打電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.42,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,暑假又得去警察局一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.60,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:01.86,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是我 暑假必須要去恰噼的地方所以不能去警局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.80,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,要被抓住的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:05.89,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.49,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以 作為替代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.50,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒問題 儘管說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.89,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我全部 都能解決給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:16.91,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我不管什麼事情 都會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.20,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.08,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.77,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,就拿這個去自首好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:36.47,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.48,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,又在玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.24,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:47.14,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明天就要測試 這樣可拿不到滿分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.19,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你也學老媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.05,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,玩一會也沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:00.77,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是的 實際上正如他所說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.39,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,你很認真 了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.47,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.56,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,上了小學後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.30,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,哥哥肯定會被你瞬間超越的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.51,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那種事情之後再也沒有發生過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.12,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.98,CN - down,Student A,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.38,CN - down,Student B,0,0,0,,哇 超過了九十分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.68,CN - down,Student C,0,0,0,,你的媽媽是醫生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.00,CN - down,Student D,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.33,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,哥哥經常得滿分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:33.51,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,為什麼做不到呢 明明養的都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:37.01,CN - down,Student E,0,0,0,,東君在學業能力測試裡是全年級第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:40.26,CN - down,Student D,0,0,0,,在全鎮是第二名 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.28,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,哥哥他是都道府縣第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:48.09,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,明明都穿著一樣 吃的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但是 也有好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.01,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這個 是我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.51,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,你不是說視力下降了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.31,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,畢竟你哥他都沒用到過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.50,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.32,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,那麼下次要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,然後 轉機到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.58,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.29,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,你真的要開始打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.09,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,都說過沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.33,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,根本不行啊 要是成績下降了可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.60,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:34.60,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,哥哥他今後 肯定會和半黑幫組織有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,作為「東診所」的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.31,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽會把夢想寄託在穩重的次子身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.54,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不對 那是他的長處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,說起來這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.96,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,都不會影響他的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.87,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,只會一直吸引著母親的擔心和關注
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我 只是 認真罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.31,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,認真的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.31,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:14.54,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,只有潤也繼承了 那聰明 與機靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:19.06,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,還有原本順滑的黑髮 他也染壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:24.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,繼承自母親的 宛如描繪般優美的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.67,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,雙眼皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:28.91,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.74,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸 啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那個女生記得是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.76,CN - down,Female student B,0,0,0,,東君 那個眼睛也是名牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.66,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是 我在眼鏡店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:44.26,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,喂 你個人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.01,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,還真若無其事天天來上學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:47.56,CN - down,Marina,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.67,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂喂 在我當班長的班裡竟然有欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,在這裡的我 為了不讓診所的名聲掃地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世同學 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.50,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我是班長 有需要的話都可以和我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.41,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:20.38,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,攸關性命的工作 是不允許失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.30,CN - down,Azuma's Mom,0,0,0,,如果什麼事情都做不到完美的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.12,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.23,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我得做完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這個時候 潤也肯定也會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,算了 反正什麼也改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.44,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:24.27,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我 連一個像媽媽的女孩 都不能讓她有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.03,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,除了東君就沒別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.00,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這次我一定會完美地完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:46.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,因為我 都這麼備受期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:50.17,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世她只剩下了我 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.53,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,那個 這樣子真的好嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.53,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,只有我行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,只有我能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.52,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,可以的吧 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:03.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這樣子肯定 能像你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,做能幫助他人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:10.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,能拯救許多人的性命 能成為醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.10,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.44,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.69,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.25,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我能依靠的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以我會一直等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:41.94,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,就算你自首進了感化院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我也會一直等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,在那期間我會去找恰噼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.00,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:48.84,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:56.29,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世你真的 不會放棄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.12,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.03,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,沒事的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:22.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,記得那天之後 她再也沒有抱過我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.15,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.90,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,這麼早你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.04,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你是殺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.28,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,給我們一家抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.88,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,就因為你一切都毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.89,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,媽媽的醫院還有我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:07.28,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,無能就算了還扯我們後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.20,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你要怎麼負起責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.57,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.29,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.77,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,果然你有心結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.76,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,所以才要好好和我說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.53,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我什麼都會聽的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.92,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你根本不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,有能力 人格好 什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,大家心裡 都只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.23,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但是 只有我 誰也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:48.61,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明我連朋友都不交一心努力 但卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:53.19,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,還有別人要求我的事情 我一件也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:58.59,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,媽媽也是 對我失望至極 放手不管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:04.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,沒有人 對我感興趣 對我有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.78,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我 已經
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.64,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,除了久世她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.95,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.91,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我也在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.69,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,剛剛我也說過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.11,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,無論什麼我都願意聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.48,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,和考試多少分一點關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.68,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,那種事情怎樣都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:34.01,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,無論是想不明白的 還是煩惱的 全都一股腦說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.15,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我很想 聽你的「說」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:40.83,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你可是 我的親弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:47.04,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,做不到的 大膽承認說「做不到」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.03,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,直樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.18,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.48,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我也不是什麼都能做到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.24,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我 玩獵人遊戲超爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:11.04,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我只在這裡告訴你 都是女朋友她一直幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:16.42,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,還有 母親她做的鬆餅點心 以前可太難吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.77,CN - down,Naoki,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.11,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.34,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,半生不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:25.45,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,但是她在值夜班前做的 放進冰箱後反而凍硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.03,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,所以她也是個努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.33,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,和你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.98,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,潤也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:46.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,這眼睛 是媽媽買給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,已經不合適但我不敢說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.94,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.10,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,還有 還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.85,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,有一件事希望哥哥能聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.57,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我不得不 告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.92,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:30.59,CN - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,聽說了嗎那間醫院的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:32.98,CN - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,好像和上次的案件有關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.63,CN - down,Neighbor B,0,0,0,,欸 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.44,CN - down,Neighbor B,0,0,0,,那麼好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.76,CN - down,Neighbor C,0,0,0,,應該是被人逼著替罪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.98,CN - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,警察也認為是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.45,CN - down,Neighbor C,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:47.00,CN - down,Neighbor A,0,0,0,,是啊是啊 我好像聽說 是他的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,東君已經不會再幫助我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.77,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:02.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,接下來要怎麼辦噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.82,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我們也應該 把真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:09.28,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸 你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:12.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:16.09,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,今天開始就放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.93,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是嗎噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.81,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.03,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,去東京
